ext-align: justify;\"><span>8. Ramirez Pacheco, Julio César &amp; Torres Román, Deni. “<em>Local and Cumulative Analysis of Self-Similar Traffic Traces</em>”. Proceedings of the 16</span><span>th </span><span>IEEE International Conference on Electronics, Communications and Computers. CONIELECOMP 2006<em>.</em></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"ecxDefault\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>9.  Munoz-Rodriguez, David; Villareal-Reyes, Salvador; Vargas-Rosales,  Cesar, Angulo-Bernal Marlenne; Torres-Roman, Deni &amp; Rizo-Dominguez  Luis; “<em>Heavy Tailed Network Delay: An Alpha-Stable</em>”, Computación y Sistemas, Vol 10, No. 1, pp 16-27, 2006. ISSN: 1405-5546</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"ecxDefault\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>10. Ramirez Pacheco, Julio C. &amp; Torres Román, Deni. “<em>A Tool for for Long-range dependent analysis via the R/S Statistic</em>”. Proceedings of the 15</span><span>th </span><span>International Conference on Computing. CIC 2006<em>.</em></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"ecxDefault\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>11. Ramirez Pacheco, Julio C. &amp; Torres Román, Deni. “<em>Accuracy of Time-Domain Algorithms for Self-Similarity: An Empirical Approach</em>”. Proceedings of the 15</span><span>th </span><span>International Conference on Computing. CIC 2006</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"ecxDefault\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>12. Ramirez Pacheco, Julio César &amp; Torres Román, Deni. “<em>R/S Statistic: Accuracy and implementations” </em>Proceedings of the 18</span><span>th </span><span>IEEE International Conference on Electronics, Communications and Computers. CONIELECOMP 2008<em>.</em></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"ecxDefault\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>13. Estrada, L.; Torres, D. &amp; Ramirez, J. “<em>Hurst Parameter Estimator based on a decomposition by aggregated series</em>”. Proceedings of the 18</span><span>th </span><span>IEEE International Conference on Electronics, Communications and Computers. CONIELECOMP 2008<em>.</em>